  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomised doublet blinded study of the effect of tablet Magnesia (laxative) on post
      operative bowel ileus after open colonic resection. Material: 56 patients in two equal
      groups. Primary endpoint: Bowel function. Secondary endpoints: Intake of food and drinks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
